<item>
            <title>[FLINK-16467] MemorySizeTest#testToHumanReadableString() is not portable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-16467</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Runing this test from master gives me:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[ERROR] Failures:
[ERROR]   MemorySizeTest.testToHumanReadableString:242
Expected: is &quot;1.001kb (1025 bytes)&quot;
     but: was &quot;1,001kb (1025 bytes)&quot;
[INFO]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The test is not locale-portable.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
